snippet.title: Fully Alive Again
snippet.description: My channel is committed to helping people build a better version of themselves after surviving narcissistic abuse. Also known as the Fully Alive Again Warrior, I aim to unapologetically expose narcissistic abuse and the effect it is having on our society. I am an independent researcher, and lifelong survivor of narcissistic abuse. My mother and 3 siblings are all narcissists – and I was in a 23 year marriage to one as well. I have lived through and recovered from all the extremes of narcissist abuse. I fully understand narcissistic abuse and the Complex PTSD it creates. I am a Post-Traumatic-Growth Coach. I use what I have learned from my research, and soul-crushing experiences to help other narcissist abuse survivors take back their life and become fully alive again. If you need support, please visit my website, Full Alive Warrior, link below. This channel is for education purposes only, not to diagnose a personality disorder.
